Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,over the ages that have stood in man's way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of realizing the absolute truth for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So he doesn't have to rely on history.
