Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes it even more comprehensible
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,in the teachings of Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive them, for they know not what they do.
