Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's essential for life
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to constantly sample what's out there
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,because it lacks energy within itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw, in our own scientific mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the explanation of the innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of all that exists.
