Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:08:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,comes out of an intrinsic biologic evolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,phenomenon of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, we don't have to come from a false forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think a lot of times, Christians strain themselves
