Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say, yes, like the mind of the child,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the little computer in all of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,will buy any software that you put in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So our little ego is nothing but
