Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,put in the hardware.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And we didn't have any say about it, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't get a chance to say okay
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to every sentence that you got programmed with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in kindergarten or throughout school
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or on the blog sites or something.
