Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to do the last slides here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just want to affirm
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that the obligation is of the teacher to the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual teaching is an obligation on the part of the teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to do his best job because he's responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to teach to the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I get emails from people who've committed to some guru somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and they want to move on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and now they're guilt-stricken because they're bound.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So a teacher doesn't bind you to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A teacher frees you from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just got one this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's afraid to leave this teacher, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and now will she lose the value of his or her, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't want a teacher who binds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one way to distinguish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
