Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So one of its values in science, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,is with consciousness research,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,you can check out a whole research design
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and know the outcome before you start it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Companies spend very, very big money on research.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Very big.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Very big.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And how easy it would be if somebody submits a research proposal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say, this calibrates at so-and-so,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and you get a weak arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You just saved that company $250 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,plus a couple of years on the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can see the great value to science
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is to use it as a guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We know the outcome of a research before it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:12:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All you need is the research design
