Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and save millions of dollars,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,time, energy, equipment, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can do the same thing with advertising.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is advertising.
