Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,about which we have been talking this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to clarify it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.42,0:23:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anybody like more elaboration on anything?
