Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.44,0:25:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Praying for people is something different
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.44,0:26:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're not saying it's your power as a healer,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.44,0:26:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
