Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.19,0:29:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So apparently three months, it's only a physical,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.19,0:29:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only a physicality, a biologic animal thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.19,0:29:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really like a humanness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.19,0:29:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,until the spirit comes in in the third month.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.19,0:29:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So there could be certainly some definition
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.22,0:29:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of why the calibrations would vary,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.22,0:29:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,whether, you know, stem cells are taken before
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.22,0:29:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,or after the third month, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.22,0:29:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an area that I have much area addition in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.82,0:29:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, the Roe versus Wade decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.82,0:29:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it created this arbitrary thing of trials
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.82,0:29:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and trimesters, and that seems to follow along
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.82,0:29:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,with this idea of the spirit coming in three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.82,0:30:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there any truth guiding the arbitrary division
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.89,0:30:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of a pregnancy to trimesters?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.89,0:30:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's sort of traditional in medicine
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.30,0:30:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to refer to them as trimesters.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.30,0:30:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And certain things are appropriate for each trimester.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.44,0:30:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We just happened to hit upon it, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.44,0:30:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because of people's guilt about abortion, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.44,0:30:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you abort a fetus less than three months,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.44,0:30:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only a physical thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.44,0:30:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not human yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.44,0:30:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it has human potential,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.52,0:30:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but nevertheless, it's not a human spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.66,0:30:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,involved in it yet, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.66,0:30:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still just an embryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.66,0:30:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what we found in research.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.66,0:30:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say, I don't have any position about it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.66,0:30:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,or don't know any of the other, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.98,0:30:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself don't feel justified to take human life
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.98,0:30:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,once it exists as human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.98,0:30:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I would not take it upon myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.98,0:30:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And the oath of Bacchus I took is not to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.98,0:31:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would not be allowed by my own medical ethics
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.98,0:31:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to do so, you know, despite the sociologic problem
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.98,0:31:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the lady has.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.98,0:31:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sociologic problem is a sociologic problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.98,0:31:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be solved sociologically,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.98,0:31:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, within its own realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.98,0:31:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Context versus content is very confusing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.91,0:31:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a way of maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.91,0:31:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,getting a little better handle on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.91,0:31:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, content is, yes, we have a slide on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.91,0:31:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Content versus context.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.06,0:31:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The content is what's within the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.06,0:31:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's defined, it's linear, demarcated, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.06,0:31:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But this doesn't happen in a vacuum.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.09,0:31:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens in an overall field.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.09,0:31:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, a field, and the field influences the consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.68,0:31:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.68,0:31:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,are certain procedures,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.68,0:32:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,violations of the rights of citizens,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.96,0:32:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,privacy, et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.96,0:32:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,are they a violation or not a violation?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.96,0:32:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So you read the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.96,0:32:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.84,0:32:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's obvious that in a time of war,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.84,0:32:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,this is appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.84,0:32:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In a time of peace, it is not appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.84,0:32:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So the context makes all the difference in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.00,0:32:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We did things during the war because we were at war
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.00,0:32:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that you can't do at peace or if you're at peace, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.00,0:32:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.00,0:32:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So the context, then, is the overall field.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.24,0:32:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, context includes intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.24,0:32:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So it brings us to situational ethics.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.29,0:32:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the courts of law.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.29,0:32:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How guilty is a person?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.29,0:32:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about culpability now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.40,0:32:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How culpable is the person?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.40,0:32:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the court of law says the context is
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.40,0:33:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a mentally retarded person
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.40,0:33:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,who thought Jesus was telling him to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.40,0:33:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That totally changes the consequences of the action.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.40,0:33:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.46,0:33:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the other condition would be a jealous lover
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.46,0:33:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,who was intoxicated and shot somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.46,0:33:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The context is completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.46,0:33:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So in one case, the jury would be lenient,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.46,0:33:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the other case, they would be more stringent
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.46,0:33:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because the context is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.46,0:33:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.65,0:33:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So context, then, is also an energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.65,0:33:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite context of consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.65,0:33:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is the emanation of the power
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.00,0:33:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in the form of energy of that which is divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.00,0:33:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which arises all creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.00,0:33:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One cubic centimeter of empty space
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.96,0:33:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,has within it more potential energy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.22,0:33:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,than the total gravity and mass of the total universe
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.22,0:34:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.39,0:34:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,One cubic inch of empty space has within it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.74,0:34:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,because, don't forget, every second
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.78,0:34:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's also the center of the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.78,0:34:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,has within it the equivalent of more E equals mc squared
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.78,0:34:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,than the total mass of the entire universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.78,0:34:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're dealing in staggering dimensions,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.19,0:34:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,staggering dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.26,0:34:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So here is the...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.90,0:34:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's really three things.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.90,0:34:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the event that's linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.90,0:34:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You take a photograph of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.00,0:34:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody running over a dog in the street, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.00,0:34:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the proximate field.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.05,0:34:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The nearest conditions is it was a rainy day,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.05,0:34:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,a rainy day,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.11,0:34:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and she had a few highballs,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.11,0:34:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,she had a few martinis.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.11,0:34:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a rainy day, she had a few martinis,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.11,0:34:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and she ran over the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.07,0:35:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the reason she had the martinis
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.07,0:35:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is her mother and father had just died,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.07,0:35:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and she was grieving.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.07,0:35:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She was trying to quiet herself, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.07,0:35:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So the even greater context was
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.07,0:35:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,although she was wrong here,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.07,0:35:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you could see...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.07,0:35:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So each factor that you add then
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.07,0:35:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,adds to the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.46,0:35:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The context, the infinite context, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.46,0:35:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is the mind of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.46,0:35:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite context is the infinite,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.46,0:35:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,infinite field of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.30,0:35:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason we talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.40,0:35:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that just as...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.61,0:35:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The radiance of divinity is absolute,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.61,0:35:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and the reason we talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.61,0:35:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness as the absolute
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.23,0:35:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is because its power is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.61,0:35:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And karmic propensities are
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.61,0:35:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,every time we make a choice or a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.73,0:35:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In the infinite field of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.73,0:35:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,which is infinite power,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.73,0:35:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we gave you an analogy of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.38,0:36:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the field of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.38,0:36:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the radiance of divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.38,0:36:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,its power is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.38,0:36:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Its power...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.38,0:36:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So the infinite...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.38,0:36:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This field here,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.38,0:36:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,its power is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.86,0:36:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.86,0:36:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thereby,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.50,0:36:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I use the analogy of an iron filing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.50,0:36:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This little iron filing is positive at one end
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.50,0:36:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and negative at the other end.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.48,0:36:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's your little karma iron filing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.48,0:36:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your little spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.48,0:36:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So every time you say yes
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.48,0:36:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to that which is integrous,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.48,0:36:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it charges you this end of your little magnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.48,0:36:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time you say yes
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.48,0:36:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to that which is not integrous,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.48,0:36:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you pull yourself down in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.48,0:36:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.48,0:36:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,as you make thousands and thousands of decisions,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.48,0:36:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,if you ever look at how many decisions you make in 24 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.48,0:36:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.48,0:36:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thousands, literally.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.48,0:36:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to choose between here or there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.48,0:36:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time you move your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.48,0:36:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got to make a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.51,0:36:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a world of the greatest karmic opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.73,0:37:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to undo the negative and to gain the positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.73,0:37:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because every time you choose integrity and truth, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.73,0:37:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you charge yourself this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.73,0:37:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and every time you choose the opposite,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.73,0:37:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you move yourself this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.73,0:37:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not happening in a vacuum.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.73,0:37:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is happening in a field of infinite power,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.73,0:37:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness of divinity itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.73,0:37:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So where you are in the overall field
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.84,0:37:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is just a consequence of that which you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.84,0:37:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why there's no need to worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.92,0:37:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,where you go after you leave the physicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.92,0:37:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.92,0:37:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.92,0:37:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So all these little iron filings then,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.92,0:37:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see the justice of God is constant.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.92,0:37:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no judgment day, isolated day.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.92,0:37:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.00,0:37:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're constantly moving closer and closer
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.09,0:37:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to divinity in its positive aspect, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.09,0:37:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and then when you refuse that divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.09,0:37:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you say, I don't believe in God,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.09,0:38:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and you become blasphemous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.09,0:38:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you go down to the bottom of the thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.09,0:38:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and you leave the body and find yourself in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.09,0:38:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,By your own choice, by your own choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.09,0:38:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To be in the complete absence of God is hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.57,0:38:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's agony beyond all descriptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.57,0:38:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've inferred it to you here a number of times
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.57,0:38:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and described my own personal experience with hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.57,0:38:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet it's far beyond the most horrible imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.44,0:38:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you can conjure up,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.65,0:38:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in which torture and all that kind of stuff is child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.65,0:38:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an agony of the denial of hope forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.42,0:38:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the state of agony,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.42,0:38:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the state of agony of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.71,0:38:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you experience forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.71,0:38:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You get what forever is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.71,0:38:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And the dread of foreverness, of damnation,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.71,0:38:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is the horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.84,0:38:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just the damnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.84,0:38:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the foreverness, forever, eternally.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.84,0:38:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally with no hope at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.03,0:39:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternal hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.63,0:39:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why I tell people,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.63,0:39:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,don't fool around, which is negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.63,0:39:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even play with those toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.76,0:39:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're radioactive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.76,0:39:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not any place you ever want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.09,0:39:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.09,0:39:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not any place you ever want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.09,0:39:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you'll never regret
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.09,0:39:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,having chosen the integrous level.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.09,0:39:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say, well, if I'd only bought that stock,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.09,0:39:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be worth this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.09,0:39:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd only done this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.09,0:39:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are all hypothetical,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.09,0:39:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're guided by our karmic propensities.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.09,0:39:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So you value some things more than personal gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.32,0:39:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fact that you value integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.32,0:39:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and truth and honesty and love
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.32,0:39:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,greater than gain
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.32,0:39:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,already moves you in the field, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.32,0:39:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, you don't have to be afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.32,0:39:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of leaving the body, because when you leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.32,0:39:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to be with that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.32,0:39:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're like the purr and love kitties
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.46,0:39:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and love puppies in your heart prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.46,0:39:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,when you leave the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.46,0:40:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,where are you going to find yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.46,0:40:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to find yourself automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.46,0:40:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,with the heart energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.46,0:40:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the heart heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.67,0:40:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's multiple heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.67,0:40:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Multiple heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.80,0:40:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of these things we'll just reaffirm,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.80,0:40:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because some people may not have been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.80,0:40:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get to that one next.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.80,0:40:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist. There's multiple heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.80,0:40:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.80,0:40:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one is the equivalent of exactly that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.80,0:40:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.80,0:40:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be afraid of when you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.80,0:40:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See, we already said,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.80,0:40:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,none of us are afraid to die
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.80,0:40:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,if we could all go over at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.80,0:40:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We did that last time, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.80,0:40:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If we all go over at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.80,0:40:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is it okay to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.80,0:40:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.80,0:40:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to go over
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.80,0:40:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,only by our little, lone selves?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.80,0:40:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.44,0:40:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're going to be with that which you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.53,0:40:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,because how else could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.53,0:40:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the iron filing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.53,0:40:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.53,0:40:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it moves out of the physicality,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.53,0:40:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's in the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.53,0:41:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And it just is with what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.53,0:41:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's multiple heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.53,0:41:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Multiple heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.53,0:41:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And all these religions that claim exclusiveness to heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.53,0:41:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,are both wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.53,0:41:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.53,0:41:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have an exclusiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.53,0:41:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to all of heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.53,0:41:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They only get their neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.53,0:41:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the pipeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.53,0:41:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're whatever that guy is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.53,0:41:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that's running for Congress,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.53,0:41:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,what do they call him?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.69,0:41:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Someplace or other.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.69,0:41:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They have their own heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.69,0:41:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to have 13 wires
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.69,0:41:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,or something to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.69,0:41:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.69,0:41:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for that heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.92,0:41:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're not one of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.92,0:41:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a Mormon, I guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.92,0:41:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're not a Mormon,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.92,0:41:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't get to go to Mormon heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.92,0:41:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that sounds okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.92,0:41:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.92,0:41:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.92,0:41:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for that heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.92,0:41:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're not one of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.92,0:41:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a Mormon, I guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.92,0:41:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're not a Mormon,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.92,0:41:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't get to go to Mormon heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.92,0:41:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that sounds okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.17,0:41:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.78,0:41:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So each sect,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.78,0:41:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,each religion,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.78,0:41:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,each denomination
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.78,0:41:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,has its own heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.78,0:41:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get into that heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.78,0:41:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So it does control the pipeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.78,0:41:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't know that Catholics
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.78,0:42:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,get into a Baptist heaven or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.32,0:42:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect that whatever you are
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.32,0:42:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in this lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.32,0:42:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in its idealized form,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.32,0:42:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,has its own dimension
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.32,0:42:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in the non-linear domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.32,0:42:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And you become attracted to it
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.32,0:42:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because like goes to like.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.32,0:42:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you merely radiate out
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.32,0:42:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.32,0:42:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be attracted
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.32,0:42:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to something that is
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.32,0:42:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,not what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.32,0:42:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.32,0:42:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm hearing is concerning
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.32,0:42:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,from this moving over.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.55,0:42:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave the body behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.69,0:43:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what did the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.21,0:43:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,say about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.21,0:43:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What did the great teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.23,0:43:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huang Po?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.30,0:43:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only your addiction
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.44,0:43:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to the linear that brings you back
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.44,0:43:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to the physical in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.44,0:43:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So let go of your identification
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.44,0:43:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and addiction to the linear,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.44,0:43:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,both attractions and aversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.44,0:43:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It fits perfectly,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.28,0:43:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,just what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.28,0:43:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.07,0:43:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.21,0:43:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.51,0:43:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.51,0:43:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.23,0:43:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That would mean you would take...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.80,0:43:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't get what you're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.51,0:44:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is the surrender of the linear...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.38,0:44:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.38,0:44:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...is my primary purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.51,0:44:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because it takes you to the...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.51,0:44:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the heavens calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.51,0:44:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,at different levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.51,0:44:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So attachment to the linear
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.26,0:44:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean you can't go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.26,0:44:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It just means that it's contextualized
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.26,0:44:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,within a decision to be loving
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.26,0:44:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and benevolent and forgiving
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.26,0:44:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and certain virtues.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.26,0:44:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean you're enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.32,0:44:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that you would be
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.32,0:44:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in a very heavenly good place.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.32,0:44:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment is something
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.32,0:44:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,different than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.32,0:44:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So the lack of awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.32,0:44:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of what that could be
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.32,0:44:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is not unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.32,0:44:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.32,0:44:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.75,0:44:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.15,0:44:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.15,0:44:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.15,0:44:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All I know
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.28,0:44:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is what the good book tells me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.28,0:44:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What she's afraid of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.40,0:44:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is she's going to take
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.40,0:44:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,her addictions along with the...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.40,0:45:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're going to take
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.40,0:45:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,your addictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.40,0:45:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your attachments.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.40,0:45:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.63,0:45:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.63,0:45:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.63,0:45:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.63,0:45:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.63,0:45:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're supposed
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.63,0:45:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to surrender them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.09,0:45:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.09,0:45:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm surrendering all to God
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.09,0:45:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and staying in that sense
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.09,0:45:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of awareness...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.09,0:45:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.09,0:45:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.09,0:45:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There would not be an awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.09,0:45:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of what would be to come as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.09,0:45:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.09,0:45:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in a transition.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.09,0:45:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the most complicated
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.09,0:45:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,hypothetical I've ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.63,0:45:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying in English?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.63,0:45:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What goes around comes around?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.63,0:45:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.63,0:45:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.63,0:45:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.63,0:45:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.63,0:45:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.63,0:45:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.63,0:45:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.88,0:45:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.88,0:45:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.88,0:45:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's making a point of the choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.88,0:45:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the choices?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.88,0:45:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the choices are...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.88,0:45:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when you make a bad decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.92,0:45:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.92,0:45:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you make a good decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.92,0:45:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you go up higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.92,0:45:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.92,0:45:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.92,0:45:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.92,0:45:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.92,0:45:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you make a bad decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.92,0:45:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you're down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.92,0:45:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if you make a good decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.92,0:45:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you're up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.92,0:45:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That counters that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.92,0:45:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you can undo negative karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.92,0:45:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're undoing that karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.92,0:45:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.92,0:45:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if you live a good life here,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.92,0:45:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're undoing
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.92,0:45:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the negative karma
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.92,0:46:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that you might have created
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.92,0:46:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.92,0:46:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.92,0:46:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the sense of bringing
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.92,0:46:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,anything with me
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.92,0:46:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is an illusion as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.92,0:46:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you want a negative karma
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.11,0:46:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,live a good life, you're not going to take all the good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.26,0:46:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to bring with you that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.84,0:46:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something external
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.17,0:46:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to what you are. So in other words, you want to get
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.11,0:46:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,rid of all this negative karma down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.11,0:46:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.82,0:46:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me have this arm a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.51,0:46:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.53,0:46:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The principle of karma
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.67,0:46:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is a factual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.28,0:46:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.71,0:46:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case we got any karma doubters.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.88,0:46:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, honey, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.05,0:47:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,End up in the letter file?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.86,0:47:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We reincarnate.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.71,0:47:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So when do we stop being
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.55,0:47:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,reincarnated and end up...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.73,0:47:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I think, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.38,0:47:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a whole field of research in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.13,0:47:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you karmically are
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.44,0:47:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,entitled to make a decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.84,0:47:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,whether you're
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.90,0:47:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,more or less compelled to follow
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.32,0:47:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,certain pathways due to your own actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.55,0:47:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you've lost the freedom of choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.42,0:47:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the hells
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.59,0:47:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,are people who've lost the freedom of choice
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.78,0:47:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're not allowed to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.94,0:47:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,change their mind
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.25,0:47:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and they have to undo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.65,0:47:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Undo it. So we see on this planet
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.17,0:47:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of people are on their way up from hell, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.19,0:47:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.63,0:47:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,learning a new way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.15,0:47:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Some make great progress. Others do make
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.32,0:47:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,very little progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.63,0:47:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Another point you suggested years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.57,0:48:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,what is that, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.19,0:48:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.07,0:48:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Resurrection?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.17,0:48:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that was a wonderful movie, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.76,0:48:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She died.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.76,0:48:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.26,0:48:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's so many years since I saw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.84,0:48:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She went over on the other side,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.53,0:48:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,right? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.61,0:48:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.09,0:48:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.53,0:48:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She was in, like, one of the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.59,0:48:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so-called bardos.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.23,0:48:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She went to one of the so-called bardos.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.05,0:48:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,B-A-R-D-O.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.75,0:48:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She was one of the bardos, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.42,0:49:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The Inner Planes, they're called.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.44,0:49:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Commonly referred to as the Inner Planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.86,0:49:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know because
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.61,0:49:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've forgotten the details of that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.88,0:49:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I remember that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.13,0:49:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it was basically true.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.57,0:49:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.13,0:49:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.28,0:49:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If they weren't in some sort of form,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.38,0:49:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,she wouldn't have recognized them anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.94,0:49:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't be waving back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.23,0:49:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see what she's
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.71,0:49:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about. Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.46,0:49:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.78,0:49:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.32,0:49:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,they're called bardos.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.51,0:49:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Inner Planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.21,0:49:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's talking about the Inner Planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.42,0:49:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the so-called Inner Planes
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.23,0:49:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,where you go in between lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.23,0:49:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to hang out
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.11,0:49:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,with your pals?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.34,0:49:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are certain realms
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.00,0:49:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,where you have the privilege of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.01,0:50:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,undoing the negative
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.76,0:50:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and gaining the positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.69,0:50:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's other realms where you do not have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.67,0:50:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to earn that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.78,0:50:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Having disputed it,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.82,0:50:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,having spit at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.90,0:50:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,having thrown it away,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.78,0:50:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you may have to go through quite a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.09,0:50:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,before you get that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.28,0:50:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,permission for choice back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.67,0:50:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.40,0:50:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,People who spit at God
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.59,0:50:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and divinity and things
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.03,0:50:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,may find that they've lost
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.21,0:50:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.98,0:50:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They've lost the freedom of choice
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.46,0:50:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,as the penalty you pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.57,0:50:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I always tell people it's not a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.88,0:50:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're about five minutes over
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.13,0:50:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can answer one more question.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.92,0:50:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, one more question.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.92,0:50:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, may we have it quickly?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.84,0:50:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.46,0:50:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.78,0:50:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this audience is over 440,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.13,0:50:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,450,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.78,0:50:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,445,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.53,0:51:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,440.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.65,0:51:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This audience is over 440.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.78,0:51:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.00,0:51:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is at 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.92,0:51:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.19,0:51:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,currently is over 204.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.63,0:51:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,204.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.65,0:51:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,205.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.32,0:51:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness of mankind is at 204.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.46,0:51:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This audience comes in
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.76,0:51:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,at a consciousness of 440.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.71,0:51:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,445.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.61,0:51:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As compared to mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.46,0:51:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize it's an extremely advanced group.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.67,0:51:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness level of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.44,0:51:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness level of America,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.11,0:51:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we've been doing that every month too,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.61,0:51:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,keeping a sharp eye on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.80,0:51:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,See if they need any kind of help
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.11,0:51:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,from us folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.96,0:51:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness level of America,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.01,0:51:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.30,0:51:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 421.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.42,0:52:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh God, it went down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.96,0:52:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It went down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.51,0:52:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.07,0:52:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's at 420.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.55,0:52:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.63,0:52:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It went down to 420.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.63,0:52:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when you look at the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.17,0:52:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,combination of
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.63,0:52:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Islamic terrorism
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.11,0:52:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,with relativism, as the Pope said,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.44,0:52:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it's an
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.11,0:52:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,enough to bring down
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.80,0:52:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Western civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.30,0:52:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.07,0:52:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.13,0:52:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.09,0:52:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the Pope's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.09,0:52:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with him right along.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.59,0:52:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the combination of the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.48,0:52:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,One opens the door for the Trojan horse
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.67,0:52:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the Trojan horse jumps out.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.78,0:52:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're recapitulating ancient Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.19,0:52:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same conflict
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.59,0:52:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,with inevitably headed in the same direction
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.73,0:52:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,for the same reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.84,0:52:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For the same reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.26,0:52:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.46,0:52:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the downside of democracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.92,0:53:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The downside.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.59,0:53:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As Socrates said,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.65,0:53:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you give freedom of speech to the people
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.03,0:53:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and freedom of the vote,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.40,0:53:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,they will bury themselves eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.57,0:53:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They will sooner or later destroy themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.36,0:53:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,because the unprivileged
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.73,0:53:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,will vote themselves all the privileges
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.46,0:53:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and they don't have the responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.09,0:53:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to respect the freedom of free speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.17,0:53:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Free speech is constructive
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.75,0:53:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's used constructively.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.78,0:53:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's destructive
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.75,0:53:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's used destructively.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.76,0:53:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,See, you can't say free speech
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.44,0:53:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is great because free speech will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.53,0:53:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say anything on today's blog sites, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.07,0:53:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To destroy yourself, destroy your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.34,0:53:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,destroy reputation, destroy companies,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.51,0:53:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,destroy integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.98,0:53:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a two-edged sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.32,0:53:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the miracles teaches, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.94,0:53:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a one-edged sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.38,0:53:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgiveness is a one-edged sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.09,0:53:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom of speech, et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.59,0:53:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is a two-edged sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.51,0:53:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can cut yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.51,0:53:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as you can cut your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.09,0:54:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have to be aware
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.11,0:54:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of what is the downside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.34,0:54:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have to be aware of what is the downside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.44,0:54:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Society, it's upside and it's downside
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.55,0:54:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we have a balanced view
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.67,0:54:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that the things we've died for
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.65,0:54:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,are fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.36,0:54:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And if misused, they'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.90,0:54:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you misuse, they'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.17,0:54:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's our cheery thought for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.44,0:54:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we do what we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.32,0:54:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have a break again?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.09,0:54:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our upbeat note.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.51,0:54:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what it means is
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.57,0:54:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,freedom is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.32,0:54:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.50,0:54:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the karmic opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.11,0:54:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of free speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.98,0:54:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're now given that with which
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.67,0:54:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you can curse God
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.09,0:54:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and blaspheme
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.40,0:54:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and destroy your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.07,0:54:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and try to destroy the souls of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.80,0:54:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're given the freedom of speech
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.21,0:54:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to stand for integrity and virtue.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.50,0:54:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If the law says you can only do this
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.80,0:54:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and not this,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.67,0:54:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no karmic merit, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.88,0:54:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The only karmic merit is
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.55,0:55:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you're free to either steal the chocolate
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.88,0:55:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,or not steal the chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.63,0:55:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's no chance to steal the chocolate,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.53,0:55:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you haven't scored anything for virtue, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.69,0:55:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So every time we calibrate it,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.30,0:55:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we get that this human life
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.92,0:55:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is the most perfect opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.34,0:55:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,for the advancement of your consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.28,0:55:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,for the gaining of positive karma
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.01,0:55:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and the undoing of negative karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.30,0:55:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, this world is perfect as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.63,0:55:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.71,0:55:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Zowie.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.13,0:55:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm honored to be with
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.48,0:55:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,such people.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.26,0:55:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.15,0:55:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be honored to be with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.26,0:55:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We are honored to be with people
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.82,0:55:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,who have gained sufficient karmic merit
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.78,0:55:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that they have been allowed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.25,0:55:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in a world such as this
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.94,0:55:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,where we have the power
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.86,0:55:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to transcend the negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.80,0:55:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Other dimensions, they have no such choice
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.90,0:56:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have earned.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.69,0:56:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can respect each other
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.30,0:56:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have earned the choice
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.13,0:56:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to gain by merit
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.03,0:56:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and to pay the price
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.32,0:56:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,by lack of merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.28,0:56:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And sure enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.96,0:56:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we do pay the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.46,0:56:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We pay with pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.09,0:56:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's one reason we grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.17,0:56:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So this group is enlightened to,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.38,0:56:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.53,0:56:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is destined to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.48,0:56:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a class of the future enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.92,0:56:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,which I've known all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.55,0:56:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the class of the future enlightened beings
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.53,0:56:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of the coming worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.05,0:56:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.73,0:56:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They can evolve and come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.13,0:56:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,evolve and come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.28,0:56:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are the teachers of the future
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.84,0:56:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,standing here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.86,0:56:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I am honored
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.36,0:56:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to be your teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.98,0:57:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure, we'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.25,0:57:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, look at the beautiful flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.25,0:57:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.73,0:57:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.23,0:57:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.23,0:57:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.23,0:57:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.23,0:57:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.23,0:57:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No question.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.23,0:57:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to sit here for one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.23,0:57:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.23,0:57:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a book by a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.71,0:57:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good God.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.96,0:57:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.96,0:57:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.96,0:57:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.98,0:57:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To laugh at yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.98,0:57:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes you immune to being laughed at by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.98,0:57:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You laugh at yourself, nobody, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.55,0:57:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,makes you immune to being laughed at by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.55,0:57:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So I should start laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.55,0:57:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How can they, how can they hit you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.01,0:57:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,where you haven't already laughed at yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.01,0:57:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why being sensitive is so neurotic, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.32,0:57:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break from being sensitive, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.32,0:57:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I want somebody who can laugh at themself.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.73,0:58:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you are short, fat, stupid and ugly, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.73,0:58:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.73,0:58:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.73,0:58:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.73,0:58:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're cheap too.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.73,0:58:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.73,0:58:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, you've talked about the experience of the total suffering of mankind at one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.73,0:58:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.73,0:58:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And you described it as a revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.73,0:58:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.73,0:58:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a divine revelation or was that more of a Luciferic?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.73,0:58:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither one.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.73,0:58:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.73,0:58:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.73,0:58:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a realization, an opening of an awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.51,0:58:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I saw the totality.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.92,0:58:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It came on spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.92,0:58:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I, you know, have been studying the endeavoring to reach the core of truth, you see, for its own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.25,0:59:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wasn't consciously thinking about any such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.63,0:59:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But then it came as a revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.88,0:59:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you see, something like 85% of mankind lives below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.05,0:59:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The amount of hell that people are experiencing is enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.05,0:59:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if you project that back in time, the totality of the suffering of mankind throughout all of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.65,0:59:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it blew me right out of being a religionist to being an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.65,0:59:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm trying to understand how to avoid making that kind of mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.65,0:59:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.26,0:59:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a way of jumping to the conclusion that there is no God.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.71,0:59:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's part of one's process.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.86,0:59:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You might see a karmic test, what you do with the revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.03,0:59:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Use that to curse God or dedicate to overcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.19,1:00:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So you could choose the high road or the low road to help relieve that suffering or to add to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.84,1:00:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.94,1:00:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be a physician.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.94,1:00:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more aligned with God.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.94,1:00:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.94,1:00:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're confronted all the time with human agony and suffering.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.90,1:00:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's like your enemy in a way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.90,1:00:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In a way, it's your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.03,1:00:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,To be subdued and beaten.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.03,1:00:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, as I listen to your lectures and I study your works,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.25,1:00:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a couple of things seem to become clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.25,1:00:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,One is that it's important to not mix up levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.25,1:00:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.25,1:00:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But another is that it is important to apply
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.25,1:00:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual truth in our lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.25,1:00:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.25,1:00:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, oftentimes people may go astray or make mistakes because
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.25,1:00:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual truth has been taken out of context and misapplied.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.25,1:00:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.25,1:01:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you speak to us a little bit about how to recognize more accurately
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.25,1:01:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,when that's being done so we don't fall into that?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.25,1:01:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than calibrating it, you see, because at a certain level of awareness you intuit it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.25,1:01:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.25,1:01:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At level 600, the opening of the third eye, the Buddhic body, the etheric body,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.25,1:01:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you have the capacity to discern appearance from essence.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.76,1:01:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.28,1:01:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be up to your spiritual erudition that you picked up from the teacher
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.28,1:01:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and the teachings and from your own spiritual study.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.55,1:01:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But after a while, you begin to intuit it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.55,1:01:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When I get a letter, I always know what the calibration is as I open the letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.80,1:01:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the energy of this already.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.80,1:01:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.80,1:01:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll say, I don't think I'll read this letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.80,1:01:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard enough of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.63,1:01:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.15,1:01:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual education.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.15,1:02:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual education is what would serve you in that stead, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.15,1:02:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.94,1:02:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.94,1:02:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Malaysia, and you left it out of your book.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.94,1:02:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.94,1:02:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where Malaysia is.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.94,1:02:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's above Singapore, below Thailand.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.94,1:02:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew where Malaysia was.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.94,1:02:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.94,1:02:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you calibrate it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.01,1:02:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Malaysia, it's between what?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.17,1:02:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just above Singapore, below Thailand.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.17,1:02:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Above Singapore.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.17,1:02:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Below Thailand.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.19,1:02:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on the other side of the globe, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.19,1:02:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly on the other side of the globe.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.19,1:02:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It took me 49 hours to get here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.19,1:02:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a mission to do Malaysia.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.36,1:02:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over at 350, 375, 370, 375, 370.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.59,1:02:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very high.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.59,1:02:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.59,1:02:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to know if you could just send a good wish to my children.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.59,1:02:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A good wish?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.59,1:02:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sending it right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.59,1:02:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.59,1:02:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.59,1:02:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.59,1:02:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Singapore ranks quite high.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.59,1:03:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.59,1:03:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,400 and something.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.59,1:03:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So that part of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.59,1:03:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.59,1:03:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sign it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.59,1:03:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Malaysia is a Muslim country.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.59,1:03:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a what country?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.59,1:03:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Muslim.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.59,1:03:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.59,1:03:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And Singapore is not.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.59,1:03:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.59,1:03:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.59,1:03:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So Singapore's higher.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.59,1:03:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.59,1:03:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Singapore is higher.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.59,1:03:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I never, I was in China, in the South China Sea, Formosa.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.71,1:03:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.71,1:03:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.71,1:03:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.71,1:03:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.71,1:03:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.71,1:03:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.71,1:03:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.71,1:03:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.75,1:03:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.75,1:03:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.75,1:03:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.75,1:03:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.75,1:03:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.75,1:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.75,1:03:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And Shanghai.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.23,1:03:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We swept mines in the East China Sea after the war, as soon as the war was over.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.23,1:03:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So I got to explore that part of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.23,1:03:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.23,1:03:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very exciting.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.23,1:03:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved the Orient.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.23,1:03:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can come to Malaysia.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.23,1:03:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come to ...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.23,1:03:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.23,1:03:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to find out where it is again.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.23,1:03:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get on the airplane.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.23,1:03:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I only see the side of the globe when I have breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.03,1:03:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I see this side of the globe.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.98,1:03:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.86,1:03:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a hand for Malaysia.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.86,1:04:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a long flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.63,1:04:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It took her 36 hours on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.63,1:04:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Need some more purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.61,1:04:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.44,1:04:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You had talked about John Paul II and John Paul.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.67,1:04:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pope?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.67,1:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.67,1:04:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.90,1:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And about...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.90,1:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The current Pope or the one right before him?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.90,1:04:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The one before?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.90,1:04:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.90,1:04:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And also you talked about Dalai Lama.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.90,1:04:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.90,1:04:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you said that if they moved on, they would not be able to manage their organization.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.90,1:04:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.90,1:04:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So how would they move on then?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.26,1:04:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If they go higher on the scale, they can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.48,1:05:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, 570 would be the ideal level for the head of a world church.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.57,1:05:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time you get into the really high 500s, you're not able to function that well.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.57,1:05:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's significant.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.57,1:05:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you get to 600, they would have to get somebody else to run the church because
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.57,1:05:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the last thing you can do to take care of all that linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.57,1:05:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.19,1:05:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So for any of us, if we move to move on, does that mean we have to give up our businesses
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.19,1:05:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,or our families and stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.19,1:05:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.19,1:05:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times where that would be a choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.19,1:05:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.40,1:05:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any time of choice where you can stay present in this life with your responsibilities
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.40,1:05:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and still evolve spiritually?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.40,1:05:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.51,1:05:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's nothing standing in your way of evolving because it's not just what
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.51,1:05:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is, but how you are with what is.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.03,1:05:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't what is, it's how you are with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.19,1:05:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say, if you're a millionaire, does that mean you can't get to heaven?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.61,1:05:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's how you hold that million.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.32,1:06:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're willing to lie for it, cheat for it, if you worship it, if you see it as the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.32,1:06:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,source of happiness, if you see it as a source of something outside yourself, you can be
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.98,1:06:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,poverty stricken and be much more materialistic than you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.98,1:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing materialistic than a millionaire to whom the million is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.98,1:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a responsibility that he has to use for the good of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.69,1:06:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Many millionaires become philanthropists because they want to turn it to a better use.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.69,1:06:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They've already fulfilled all the personal needs and another million doesn't mean a thing
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.69,1:06:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.55,1:06:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that the Dalai Lama is attached to his managing his...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.55,1:06:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't say that he was attached, but he's suitable for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.59,1:06:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to be a swimming team, you've got to be a certain length, a certain stroke.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.53,1:06:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just suitable for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.88,1:06:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The most suitable for a world church would be around 570.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.88,1:07:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By 590, you're not going to be that interested in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.88,1:07:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Below that, you won't have enough spiritual power to head a world-sized church.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.01,1:07:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,570 was probably ideal, you see.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.01,1:07:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time you get to 600, you bliss out.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.01,1:07:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know why this body is still here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.42,1:07:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because at 600, you're invited to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.42,1:07:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is perfect, bliss complete, and total fulfillment.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.42,1:07:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Except you've made some karmic agreement before this lifetime, which is what I get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.96,1:07:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what went on with this entity here, because of a prior agreement.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.96,1:07:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that there was something to do with that, because you don't have to come back in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.96,1:07:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But some come back in the world, but not many.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.96,1:07:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Most leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.96,1:07:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,50% leave the minute they hit 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.15,1:07:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So for this group that you said was mostly teachers in this life, next life,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.15,1:07:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,have they made a commitment to stay for mankind?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.15,1:08:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of them will make that choice, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.84,1:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.84,1:08:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.84,1:08:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It is good.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.84,1:08:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not an obligation.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.84,1:08:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like when Sir Alex Fleming discovered what penicillin could do.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.85,1:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He saw what it could do.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.85,1:08:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he didn't have to do what he did.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.92,1:08:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He felt his being a member of the family of man, here was something of great benefit.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.27,1:08:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't rest until he knew somebody picked up the ball.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.27,1:08:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So the same with consciousness research.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.27,1:08:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,To be able to tell the truth from falsehood is understood by only 15% of the people who hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.27,1:08:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the great majority of the people who even after I've said it to them 20 times don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.42,1:08:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have an instant capacity to tell the truth from where? Falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.42,1:08:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,About anything anywhere in time, about any subject whatsoever with very few things.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.42,1:08:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people get that?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.00,1:09:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.00,1:09:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you last time.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.00,1:09:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He said something about...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.00,1:09:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.00,1:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Something simple like don't eat sugar and chocolates and you won't get depression.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.00,1:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remembered it for one month and then I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.00,1:09:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I listened to your CD and I remembered it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.00,1:09:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a number of repetitions.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.00,1:09:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we repeat it. We keep going back over it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.00,1:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want people to get it by familiarity.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.00,1:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not by linear memorization.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.00,1:09:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.35,1:09:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I read...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.35,1:09:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a new car.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.35,1:09:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You ever get the manual that goes to the new car?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.35,1:09:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd have to take a month out from work.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.35,1:09:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,24 hours a day reading all this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.35,1:09:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead you have the salesman show you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.35,1:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the on off?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.35,1:09:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.35,1:09:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how do you make the windows go up and down?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.35,1:09:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So you learn by familiarity.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.35,1:09:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So the reason I'm somewhat repetitious is it becomes sort of an automatic knowingness in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.35,1:10:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Without having to go through the linear description of reading the operator's manual.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.35,1:10:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I've read your books many times.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.35,1:10:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for the last one.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.35,1:10:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But the practice of it is not easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.35,1:10:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that one thing that you would say to each of us?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.35,1:10:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That if you keep practicing that one thing...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.35,1:10:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets easier and easier.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.35,1:10:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The resistance, don't take it personally.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.35,1:10:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not you personally resisting.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.35,1:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You personally have decided already to transcend it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.35,1:10:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ego fighting for survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.76,1:10:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking the ego to give up what it's learned is necessary for survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.82,1:10:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're pitting your new right brain with the Kundalini energy against your old animal left brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.85,1:10:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose instinctual says, bury your teeth and growl and kill your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.85,1:10:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, even if I have that thought, I don't want to have that thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.11,1:10:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.11,1:10:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.11,1:10:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you talked about earlier...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.11,1:10:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you assimilate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.11,1:10:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that's just my animal nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.11,1:10:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God, because without my animal nature, I wouldn't be here complaining about my animal nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.01,1:11:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have to love the little animal in us.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.01,1:11:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if it wasn't for the little animal in us, we wouldn't be here to complain about the little animal in us.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.01,1:11:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.64,1:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan, can you make sure that they lean into the microphone?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.03,1:11:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could, everybody asking a question, lean further into the microphone so that the satellite room can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.28,1:11:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.28,1:11:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.97,1:11:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doug.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.97,1:11:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do teachers of Advaita teach less on purification but more on sort of disidentification with the ego?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.97,1:11:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the false sense of personal doership?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.97,1:11:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.97,1:11:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Start over slower.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.97,1:11:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.97,1:11:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.97,1:11:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.97,1:11:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of teachers of non-duality, they don't really...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.97,1:11:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of teachers of non-duality?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.97,1:11:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.97,1:11:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.97,1:11:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.97,1:12:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't emphasize purification to the same extent that they emphasize the false sense of personal doership.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.97,1:12:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.97,1:12:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That there's no thinking behind thoughts or behind actions.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.97,1:12:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.97,1:12:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So is purification of the personality really necessary to reach enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.97,1:12:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's no contradiction between them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.97,1:12:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, not to say there's separate paths.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.97,1:12:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But, for instance, Ramesh Bhalsikar teaches there's just a sense of personal doership.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.97,1:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.97,1:12:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And he says instead of trying to go out and purify your personality, he's saying to analyze your actions until you come to the firm conviction that you are not the doer.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.97,1:12:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of that technique?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.13,1:12:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a faster way.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.13,1:12:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way of non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.13,1:12:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.13,1:12:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.13,1:12:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm asking.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.13,1:12:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I teach in non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.89,1:12:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.89,1:12:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The direct way through consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.89,1:12:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you don't have to bathe every morning in the Ganges to accomplish it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.06,1:12:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.06,1:12:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The upside of that is you don't have to bathe in the Ganges.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.06,1:12:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The downside of it is you don't get the blessing of bathing in the water of the Ganges.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.06,1:12:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the water of the Ganges?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.06,1:12:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvary is over 500, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.06,1:12:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite dead bodies, garbage.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.52,1:12:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Malaysia girl forgot her picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.52,1:12:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the water of the Ganges is over 500.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.52,1:12:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.14,1:13:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.30,1:13:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.30,1:13:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.30,1:13:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.30,1:13:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.30,1:13:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.35,1:13:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.35,1:13:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.35,1:13:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.35,1:13:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.35,1:13:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.35,1:13:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.22,1:13:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.22,1:13:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.22,1:13:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.22,1:13:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody has been sanctified by the devotion over the centuries of the faithful.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.34,1:13:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.19,1:13:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.18,1:13:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She cut in line there, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.35,1:13:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She did cut it now, did he?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.60,1:13:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.84,1:13:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm up here because I'm terrified to be up here and that's why.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.02,1:13:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.02,1:13:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.02,1:13:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.02,1:13:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.02,1:13:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Being in front of large crowds of people that I don't know just sends me into major panic
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.06,1:13:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.06,1:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.06,1:13:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.26,1:13:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,me is my having a camera pointed at me is my second biggest fear. You can't pay attention to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.69,1:14:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. It doesn't make any, it doesn't make any matter what they think. If they think you're good,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.80,1:14:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,they're stupid. If they think you're bad, they're uninformed. So why pay attention?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.43,1:14:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get my picture taken with you so I can get over that one also? Oh golly whiz.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.28,1:14:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, speaking phobia. I had a speaking phobia when I was young. And one time I was presenting
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.10,1:14:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,a case to, when I was an intern to the whole medical staff of the hospital. And once a month
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.11,1:14:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we had a medical staff meeting. So I'm presenting this case and as I get through about two-thirds
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.34,1:14:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of the first page of the case, I knew my voice wasn't going to last the rest of the page. So
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.73,1:14:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I concluded it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.39,1:14:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and the medical audience went
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.88,1:14:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,they thought I was done
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.75,1:15:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned nobody's listening to you
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.65,1:15:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a true story
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.36,1:15:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,they applauded, isn't that funny
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.28,1:15:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,did you hear what she was talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.06,1:15:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he didn't know what you were talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.63,1:15:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.71,1:15:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we project our fears out into the world
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.22,1:15:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you always have to ask yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.98,1:15:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I look at myself as I'm answerable to God
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.94,1:15:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,at all times I'm answerable to God
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.18,1:15:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for what are my choices and what I've become
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.03,1:15:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,hi doc
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.13,1:15:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,my question is about the experience or edge of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.77,1:15:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,does that mean one transcends
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.02,1:15:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of existence itself
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.43,1:15:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.68,1:16:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you become the witness
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.64,1:16:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to the existence of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.73,1:16:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you become the witness to the phenomena
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.38,1:16:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but there is no entity doing the experiencing
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.65,1:16:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so you realize it's a sentence without a subject
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.57,1:16:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the phenomena is happening of its own
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.73,1:16:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes just as an awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.00,1:16:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not trying to accomplish that realization
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.34,1:16:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you're walking along and pedaling your bicycle
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.61,1:16:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and listening to the birds
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.06,1:16:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and suddenly you realize it's all happening spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.47,1:16:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.18,1:16:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,besides being the experiencer
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.52,1:16:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the reason you're identifying with it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.59,1:16:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is because the ego juices the experiencer
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.59,1:16:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it wants
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.63,1:16:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it's more than just experience
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.14,1:16:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it wants to experience experience
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.94,1:16:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a subtlety
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.35,1:16:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,meditation you'll get it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.13,1:16:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you can watch the movie
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.98,1:16:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,or you can be wanting to be the one who watches the movie
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.63,1:16:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.10,1:16:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,may I have a picture
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.51,1:17:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.96,1:17:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,he wants a picture
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.27,1:17:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,give him a picture ticket
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.18,1:17:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a dollar and a quarter
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.98,1:17:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,extra fifty cents for a picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.98,1:17:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.35,1:17:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,give him a picture ticket a dollar and a quarter
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.89,1:17:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,extra fifty cents, I smile
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.89,1:17:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,hi
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.81,1:17:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.89,1:17:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to have a lot of intellectual curiosity
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.10,1:17:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,like my
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.21,1:17:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,like I'll be listening to you and my mind will kind of wander off on
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.59,1:17:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,something sort of I think ultimately irrelevant of what
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.59,1:17:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say that's actually going to help me
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.59,1:17:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,with my spiritual growth
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.59,1:17:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and how to, my question is how to
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.59,1:17:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,um
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.59,1:17:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,not go there
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.97,1:17:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,well each
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.97,1:17:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I would look at each piece of information of equal value
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.39,1:17:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because you don't know when you're going to need it
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.14,1:18:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,something I never paid any attention to in this entire lifetime
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.94,1:18:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,what I call the final doorway came out of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.94,1:18:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,came out of nowhere-ness
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.61,1:18:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,not from any place, not from any entity, not from any mind, not from any memory
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.06,1:18:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it was just a knowingness already present within the space
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.00,1:18:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't know what's valuable or not
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.00,1:18:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so don't weigh it
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.00,1:18:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,mostly what you don't think is too valuable right now
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.00,1:18:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is someday you'll be walking down a path and wow you get it
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.15,1:18:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say, oh, uh-huh
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.15,1:18:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so you build up a store of knowledge
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.46,1:18:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's one part of spiritual endeavor
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.75,1:18:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is you build up a store of knowledge of teachers, teachings, pathways, religions
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.75,1:18:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,different ways of looking at it
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.75,1:18:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,there are ten thousand pathways to God
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.89,1:18:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,ten thousand
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.89,1:18:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that'd take a while to check them all out, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.23,1:18:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.23,1:19:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have one other quick question to ask you
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.23,1:19:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard you talk to people about
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.23,1:19:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,with being in the process of like moving out of depression
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.23,1:19:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,healing, transcending it
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.23,1:19:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and you talked about staying off sugar
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.23,1:19:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that, yeah, you can try that
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.23,1:19:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been going about it
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.23,1:19:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've looked at different like books and cookbooks even
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.23,1:19:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I like food
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.23,1:19:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wanted to find yummy stuff
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.23,1:19:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and a lot of them say like low fat
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.23,1:19:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,no caffeine
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.23,1:19:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and some of them, I've got contradictory though
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.23,1:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,some of them say like low fat
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.23,1:19:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the next one will say eat milkshakes and have veal for breakfast
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.23,1:19:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you're talking about a sugar-free diet
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.23,1:19:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.23,1:19:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all that got to do with sugar-free diet?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.23,1:19:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm wondering
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.23,1:19:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've looked at hypoglycemia diets
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.23,1:19:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and so fat doesn't
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.23,1:19:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.23,1:19:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.23,1:19:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay away from sugar
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.23,1:19:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You live on protein and fat
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.23,1:19:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and you avoid sugar especially on an empty stomach
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.23,1:19:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.23,1:19:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you do eat something sweet
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.23,1:19:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.19,1:19:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The best sugar is fructose
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.19,1:19:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Fructose is fruit sugar
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.19,1:20:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not create an insulin response
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.19,1:20:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.19,1:20:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the health food store
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.19,1:20:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,they have fructose candy bars
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.19,1:20:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and fructose sweets
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.57,1:20:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So stay away from like Splenda
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.57,1:20:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact it's more sweet than glucose or dextrose
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.57,1:20:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.57,1:20:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But it does not release insulin
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.57,1:20:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Fructose
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.57,1:20:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can sweeten anything with fructose
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.57,1:20:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.68,1:20:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Calorically I think it's about the same
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.68,1:20:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.68,1:20:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't trigger insulin response
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.68,1:20:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.68,1:20:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.68,1:20:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.68,1:20:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the first barrel of fructose in the United States
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.15,1:20:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was shipped to me from Scandinavia
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.15,1:20:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.14,1:20:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sign it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.14,1:20:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In return for which I wrote the forward of a book for somebody
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.43,1:20:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,who had written about the value of fructose in various ways
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.43,1:20:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I wrote the forward they would ship me a barrel
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.46,1:20:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the first barrel in the United States
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.46,1:20:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So we had it all packaged up in little pound packages
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.46,1:20:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for our patients with hypoglycemia
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.46,1:20:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that they could put fructose on their cereal in the morning
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.46,1:20:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.46,1:21:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a normal life
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.53,1:21:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk about an experiment that I had
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.53,1:21:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all I want to thank God
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.53,1:21:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to lean forward
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.53,1:21:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on you got to get up next to those things
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.53,1:21:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all I want to thank God for me being here
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.53,1:21:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thank God for you
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.53,1:21:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reading The Eye of the Eye and The Power of Now
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.40,1:21:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I went to this class
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.40,1:21:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And the class was about staying prayed up
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.69,1:21:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So the teacher says
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.89,1:21:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say you love your God with all your heart
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.89,1:21:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,With all your soul and with all your might
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.89,1:21:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So I go home and I sit in my green back chair
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.89,1:21:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I get comfortable
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.89,1:21:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I breathe
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.92,1:21:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She said breathe in too
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.92,1:21:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So I breathe in
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.92,1:21:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I love God with all of my heart
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.19,1:21:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,With all of my soul
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.19,1:21:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,With all of my might
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.19,1:22:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This energy took control of me
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.59,1:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Energy
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.59,1:22:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I would say it
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.59,1:22:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was said in my sleep
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.59,1:22:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When I turned around
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.59,1:22:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,At night
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.59,1:22:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.59,1:22:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And I played this little game with myself
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.59,1:22:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to see how long I could go without thinking
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.73,1:22:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So a thought came to my mind
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.73,1:22:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I would blink it out
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.28,1:22:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would say
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.28,1:22:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I love my God with all of my soul
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.28,1:22:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,With all of my heart
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.28,1:22:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,With all of my might too
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.05,1:22:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.05,1:22:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reading your book
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.05,1:22:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I felt your presence
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.75,1:22:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy from you was in my home
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.75,1:22:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Things got better
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.77,1:22:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.02,1:22:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were going to say somebody stole the chocolate out of your pantry
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.02,1:23:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And this presence was with me
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.38,1:23:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And it grew
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.38,1:23:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I knew I was going to a place I had never been before
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.56,1:23:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence got so strong it hurt my ears
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.56,1:23:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And the birds
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.72,1:23:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the background music came forth
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.72,1:23:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah I got where you were
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.72,1:23:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sitting on my patio
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.72,1:23:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And it had been raining
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.72,1:23:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked down
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.71,1:23:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a worm
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.71,1:23:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I could see the worm suffering
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.28,1:23:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I could see everything around me
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.28,1:23:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We was all connected to God
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.28,1:23:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We was from the same source
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.53,1:23:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This energy got into my hands
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.67,1:23:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so marvelous
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.77,1:23:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.77,1:23:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I got up in the morning I was going to work
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.65,1:23:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And there it was
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.42,1:23:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was still
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.55,1:23:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was still?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.55,1:23:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was still and silent
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.55,1:23:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I stood in my bedroom
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.55,1:23:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And everything was silent
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.55,1:24:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I knew I was in the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.55,1:24:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew you were a child of God?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.97,1:24:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I was in the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.97,1:24:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.97,1:24:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I got you
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.97,1:24:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.97,1:24:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This feeling came over me to leave
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.53,1:24:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I go
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.30,1:24:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave I got grandkids
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.61,1:24:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I didn't go
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.09,1:24:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But then this fear came over me
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.25,1:24:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear was total terror
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.25,1:24:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.25,1:24:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear was terror
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.25,1:24:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The terror the fear
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.25,1:24:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She turned down the
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.25,1:24:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh the chance to go
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.81,1:24:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The chance to go
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.81,1:24:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.81,1:24:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the fear came up?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.81,1:24:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.81,1:24:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.81,1:24:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,After that
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.81,1:24:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah I was there
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.81,1:24:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the fear came
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.81,1:24:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.81,1:24:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And this energy
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.81,1:24:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt like energy
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.81,1:24:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This energy was in my home
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.81,1:24:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was extremely scary
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.93,1:24:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But now at the point I am now
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.93,1:25:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though God is in me
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.65,1:25:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's more dormant sort of
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.65,1:25:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,More what?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.65,1:25:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dormant
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.65,1:25:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's there you know
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.65,1:25:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.65,1:25:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She had a real high experience
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.65,1:25:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she's kind of come back down
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.65,1:25:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah yeah yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.65,1:25:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah that's a revelation yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.75,1:25:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah so that's what you meant with
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.75,1:25:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of the self with the capital S
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.88,1:25:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As the ego diminishes takes over
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.88,1:25:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And you get periodic
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.88,1:25:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Like an inner radiance
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.88,1:25:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.88,1:25:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Inner radiance comes up
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.88,1:25:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes like a light
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.88,1:25:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And then sometimes it stays
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.42,1:25:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it diminishes
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.42,1:25:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it goes away
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.42,1:25:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And doesn't return for a while
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.42,1:25:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's other things
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.42,1:25:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to accomplish in the meantime
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.42,1:25:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right come back
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.42,1:25:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If that light
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.55,1:25:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That dazzling state stays
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.55,1:25:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you don't accomplish anything further
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.55,1:25:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In the world you know generally
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.55,1:25:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see why
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.55,1:25:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take you out
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.55,1:25:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's hard to
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.55,1:25:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see things that I didn't see before
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.55,1:25:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.55,1:25:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a revelation
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.55,1:25:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.55,1:25:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's hard to deal with certain things
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.55,1:25:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That I see
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.55,1:25:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because people don't know what they're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.55,1:25:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You do well
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.64,1:25:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep praying
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.64,1:25:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.64,1:25:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.64,1:25:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.64,1:25:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.64,1:25:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.64,1:26:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.64,1:26:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.64,1:26:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.64,1:26:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.86,1:26:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.86,1:26:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.86,1:26:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.98,1:26:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.98,1:26:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.98,1:26:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.98,1:26:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.98,1:26:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.92,1:26:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah the field comes up of its own
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.81,1:26:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.81,1:26:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It was angelic
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.06,1:26:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think one of my angels
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.06,1:26:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Visitation of an angel you know
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.34,1:26:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She was visited by the angelic you know
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.68,1:26:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She was consciously aware of the presence of the angelic
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.68,1:26:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm honest about it
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.31,1:26:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to admit that
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.31,1:26:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes when things don't go my way
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.31,1:26:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A feeling of resentment will come up
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.31,1:26:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.31,1:26:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To me
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.31,1:26:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,towards life or fate or towards God.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.14,1:26:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to articulate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.28,1:27:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But yeah, so I'm wondering, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.30,1:27:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,how do I transcend that?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.28,1:27:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.59,1:27:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.81,1:27:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, just to keep applying spiritual principles,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.50,1:27:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to see it differently, to experience it differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.81,1:27:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of resisting it, you welcome it
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.02,1:27:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and forgive yourself for being that which you are, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.30,1:27:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,See, a lot of people out of guilt
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.68,1:27:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,will repress and suppress such things
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.61,1:27:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of facing them.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.68,1:27:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you look to see what aspect of yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.35,1:27:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is that coming up, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.31,1:27:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And you pray to outgrow that aspect of yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.00,1:27:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask what aspect of yourself that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.11,1:27:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What role that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.97,1:27:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The trouble I always had was with the spiritual knight.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.31,1:28:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He was always getting mad and indignant at evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.89,1:28:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I wanna thank both of you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.02,1:28:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I came up here for two reasons.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.60,1:28:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,One, I like being close to the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.06,1:28:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other is I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.50,1:28:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If your life's karma gave you an autistic child
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.80,1:28:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,who's low functioning, and, let's say,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.57,1:28:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,plausibly below the level of 200, do you have any advice?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.50,1:28:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,One has a child who calibrates below 200?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.80,1:28:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's autistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.00,1:28:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you try to be the best possible parent you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.57,1:28:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all, to overcome those proclivities, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.17,1:28:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can engender a love of beauty, of music, of church going, of alignment with integrity,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.38,1:28:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,alignment with integrity as people, join the Boy Scouts, the Girl Scouts, people laugh at that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.61,1:28:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Boy Scouts and the Girl Scouts calibrate higher than about 90% of people in America.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.96,1:29:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But if his...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.65,1:29:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,460, 480.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.77,1:29:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all the things you can to add the structure of integrity and the pleasure in fulfilling one's potentiality, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.25,1:29:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If his manifestations are noisy and hand-flapping and non-verbal and kind of disruptive to other people.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.80,1:29:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How old?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.02,1:29:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,16.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.61,1:29:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,16?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.15,1:29:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.07,1:29:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a treatable condition?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.97,1:29:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.77,1:29:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen progress past a certain point.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.22,1:29:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.77,1:29:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still in school?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.10,1:29:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He goes to a special school for autistic children.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.81,1:29:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.22,1:29:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.50,1:29:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he's a special child with special needs.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.47,1:29:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.76,1:29:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now you're making...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.84,1:29:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.14,1:29:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.39,1:29:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting him in a diagnostic category.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.57,1:29:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you do what you can on every level, the same as what you would with anybody else, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.53,1:29:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are certain, obviously, karmic propensities that came forth in this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.93,1:30:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And certain things that can only be learned perhaps by the entity except in this particular form.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.39,1:30:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you bless it for whatever its karmic purpose may be.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.89,1:30:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I have a picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.98,1:30:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be difficult for the mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.26,1:30:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll push you towards sainthood quicker.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.86,1:30:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a rambunctious child, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.77,1:30:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.36,1:30:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.77,1:30:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.85,1:30:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, if one intends enlightenment, is it best to envision this lifetime or just forget timing and leave it all up to God?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.97,1:30:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.28,1:30:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I would forget about the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.02,1:31:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what the work is.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.76,1:31:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what the pathway is.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.92,1:31:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you just do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.80,1:31:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, there's no way you can rate your progress because just when you think you're doing the worst,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.77,1:31:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you can suddenly break through into a realm that is beyond anything heretofore.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.19,1:31:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's no way of guessing, you know, where you really are with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.80,1:31:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The best thing is to just persevere.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.73,1:31:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Persevere with faith that you're being attracted by your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.81,1:31:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,See, most people consider themselves propelled by their past.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.25,1:31:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They never realize that your destiny, which you've chosen by your own commitment and alignment, is what's pulling you towards the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.18,1:31:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not being driven to enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.14,1:31:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You are being pulled towards it because of your attraction, because you're having said yes to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.75,1:31:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you set the machinery in motion when you decided that you would like to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.63,1:31:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't such a light decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.09,1:32:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a heavy one.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.55,1:32:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because now it realigns your whole life, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.82,1:32:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your whole life is now being pulled in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.06,1:32:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you don't have to look at it as though I, of myself, alone, have to drive myself to the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.53,1:32:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The future is pulling you, so you let go resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.15,1:32:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the easy way.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.98,1:32:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go resisting being pulled towards the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.69,1:32:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to drive yourself to see the beauty of all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.47,1:32:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The beauty of all that exists has a magnetic attraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.06,1:32:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, look at that rose.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.52,1:32:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.13,1:32:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really look into that rose, you're not going to get off its stage here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.93,1:32:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And neither am I.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.22,1:32:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.48,1:32:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the color is stunning.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.18,1:32:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Its perfection is stunning.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.03,1:32:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The color is stunning.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.47,1:33:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And its stillness, its stillness is perfection.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.64,1:33:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The absolute perfection.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.84,1:33:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you see it there, then the next thing you know is you see it here.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.15,1:33:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you see it here.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.57,1:33:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you see it here.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.89,1:33:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you realize that it's not different than what you are, that you are also perfect at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.60,1:33:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the perfect expression of that which you are at this instant.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.52,1:33:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good enough?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.13,1:33:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good enough?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.06,1:33:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.52,1:33:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.88,1:33:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Except we don't have to water you every day like the rose.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.47,1:33:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the most incredible rose.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.27,1:33:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's just unbelievable.
